:: Start
~ gold = 500
~ sword_price = 100
~ shield_price = 80

+ [Go to shop] -> Shop

:: Shop
You have {gold} gold.

+ [Buy Sword for {sword_price} gold] -> BuyItem("Sword", sword_price)
+ [Buy Shield for {shield_price} gold] -> BuyItem("Shield", shield_price)
+ [Leave] -> Start

:: BuyItem(item_name, price)
~ gold = gold - price

You bought {item_name} for {price} gold!
You now have {gold} gold left.

+ [Back to shop] -> Shop
